N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 333.1 - Transmittal of ballot

State Regulations

The boards of elections shall transmit a military ballot, together with an envelope bearing the statement of the military voter and a
self-addressed return envelope (requiring no postage) to each military voter
whose name has been entered in the register of voters or on the registration
records. Notes
